      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm having a weird issue with my shopify theme. on mobile the product image is overlapping the title text like it's just sitting right on top of it. i tried changing the padding but it didn't do much. here is my css snippet for the product header:\n\n.product-header {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  margin-bottom: 20px;\n}\n\n.product-image-wrapper {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: auto;\n}\n\n.product-info {\n  padding: 15px;\n}\n\nany idea why it's breaking on smaller screens?",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "hey i'm having a weird issue with my shopify theme. on mobile the product image is overlapping the title text like it's just sitting right on top of it. i tried changing the padding but it didn't do much. here is my css snippet for the product header:\n\n.product-header {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  margin-bottom: 20px;\n}\n\n.product-image-wrapper {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: auto;\n}\n\n.product-info {\n  padding: 15px;\n}\n\nany idea why it's breaking on smaller screens?",
      "beast_suffix": "",
      "targeted_response_start_logprob": 0.0
    },
